By the way, in case he changes the rules again, all of this is  technically legal within these rules:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
ules:<br>
<br>
    * Any zone can be used up to two times.<br>
    * Count a zone twice if you visit it twice<br>
    * You may not use gate, teleportation spells, or take a boat.<br>
    * A zone 'line' can only be used once.<br>
    * Zones that have either a different zone in and zone out location is allowed.<br>
    * There is more than one answer, and you may find a better one than I have listed.<br>
* Getting a translocate via Nexus Portal is not allowed<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
